        <h2 class="stage-title">The cohort settles into a new rhythm. Results arrive on Adam&apos;s desk in trend. Stable patients stay in surveillance. Threshold breaches escalate. The clinic now sees the patients who clinically need to be seen, not every patient by default. <span class="hm-witness" data-moment="adam-s5"></span></h2>

