        </div>

        <div class="old-way">
          <div class="old-way-label">The old end-state</div>
          <div class="old-way-body">Cohort capped by clinic capacity. Drop-outs growing with cohort age. Routine bloods consuming consultant time. The clinically interesting patients waiting for an appointment behind the clinically uneventful ones. Surveillance failing the patients it was designed to protect.</div>
        </div>

