            <div class="careteam-text">Adam and his MDT, running a larger surveillance cohort with no clinic-capacity penalty. Catherine, his Trust commissioner, seeing released outpatient slots flow into elective recovery. Mark and the other men in the cohort, staying in surveillance, getting on with their lives.</div>
